These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, sudoku, board-games, puzzles
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, bridge, backgammon
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, 7up, iced-tea
House: gothic-revival, modern, futuristic, cape-cod
1. the person drinking juice is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the person drinking juice is the gothic-revival house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | puzzles   | woodworking  | board-games  |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | backgammon    | snooker      | bridge    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | 7up | sprite |
| House     | cape-cod  | gothic-revival       | modern    | futuristic     |

