.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, swisher, tiparillo, ritmeester
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, banana, lemon, orange
City: hamburg, san-francisco, edinburgh, marseilles
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, australian, canadian
1. the canadian is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the turkish##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
5. the person eating orange is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the thai##2
6. the canadian is between the person eating orange and the person traveling to marseilles##2
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
8. the person eating banana is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
9. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | swisher    | tiparillo  | bluemaster    |
| Food   | cabbage      | banana  | orange  | lemon |
| City           | marseilles      | edinburgh       | san-francisco      | hamburg       |
| Nationality         | turkish    | canadian | australian | thai |

